# Fault: a sofa straddling the partition between rooms A and B (well past the 30 mm slack).
# Raises: W_FURNITURE_WALL_COLLISION.
# Heals with: arch repair — the geometric corrector pushes the piece off the wall into a
#   clear position in one room (ADR 0006: a source-to-source move, not a fix span edit).
plan "Furniture Through Wall" {
  units mm
  grid 50
  wall exterior  thickness 200 { (0,0) (8000,0) (8000,4000) (0,4000) close }
  wall partition thickness 100 { (4000,0) (4000,4000) }
  room id=a at (0,0)    size 4000x4000 label "A"
  room id=b at (4000,0) size 4000x4000 label "B"
  furniture sofa at (3200,1000) size 1000x900
}
